{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7846027197","title":"就左派队伍问题和张春桥、姚文元的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"40801c2a49","index":0,"year":1966,"month":10,"day":1,"articleId":"7846027197"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"471a503675","name":"张春桥","type":"人物"},{"id":"92a8a42842","name":"姚文元","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"2413ac6eb3","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"7846027197","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这次谈话是1966年国庆节晚上在天安门上看焰火休息时进行的，张春桥1967年6月16日在上海革委会扩大会议上传达此次谈话情况时还补充说：这是指世界观的改造，不是指一般的表现，是指世界观里有较多的马列主义、毛泽东思想。要完全的马列主义、毛泽东思想就更难了。"}],"contents":[{"id":"98de789db4","type":"title","text":"就左派队伍问题和张春桥、姚文元的谈话叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"7846027197"},{"id":"2413ac6eb3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：你看左派有多少答：上海好一点，左派队伍大。毛：多大？答：工人有40万、50万、60万。毛：左派不会多，大概占10%。答：后期可能多一点。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"7846027197"}],"page":{"id":"062e810418","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"7846027197","start":87,"end":87}}}},"__N_SSG":true}